  "prompt": "Which are the top architects in pune?",
  "response": "Pune is home to several renowned architects and architectural firms known for their innovative designs and contributions to the city's urban landscape. While the \"top\" architects can be subjective and depend on specific criteria, here are some well-known architects and firms in Pune:\n\n### 1. **Christopher Charles Benninger**  \n   - Founder of **Christopher Charles Benninger Architects (CCBA)**.  \n   - Known for sustainable and contextually sensitive designs.  \n   - Notable projects: **Maharashtra Chamber of Commerce, YMCA, and Suzlon One Earth** (Pune).  \n\n### 2. **Himanshu Roy**  \n   - Principal Architect of **Studio HA** (formerly Himanshu Roy Architects).  \n   - Specializes in contemporary residential and commercial projects.  \n\n### 3. **Parul Zaveri and Nimish Patel**  \n   - Founders of **Abhikram**.  \n   - Known for eco-friendly and culturally rooted designs.  \n   - Projects include heritage conservation and sustainable architecture.  \n\n### 4. **Ninad Tipnis**  \n   - Founder of **JTCPL Designs**.  \n   - Focuses on urban planning, architecture, and interior design.  \n\n### 5. **Bijoy Jain**  \n   - Founder of **Studio Mumbai**.  \n   - Though based in Mumbai, his work influences architects in Pune. Known for handcrafted, sustainable designs.  \n\n### 6. **Kishore Dhotre**  \n   - Founder of **Kishore Dhotre Architects**.  \n   - Known for residential, commercial, and institutional projects.  \n\n### 7. **Sanjay Puri**  \n   - Founder of **Sanjay Puri Architects**.  \n   - Based in Mumbai but has projects in Pune. Known for innovative and contemporary designs.  \n\n### 8. **Sameep Padora**  \n   - Founder of **sP+a (Sameep Padora & Associates)**.  \n   - Known for modern and experimental designs.  \n\n### 9. **Deepak Guggari**  \n   - Principal Architect of **Deepak Guggari Architects**.  \n   - Specializes in residential and hospitality projects.  \n\n### 10. **Samira Rathod**  \n   - Founder of **Samira Rathod Design Atelier**.  \n   - Known for unconventional and artistic designs.  \n\n### Notable Firms in Pune:  \n- **Kothari Associates**: Specializes in residential and commercial projects.  \n- **Sustainable Habitat Foundation**: Focuses on eco-friendly architecture.  \n- **Prasanna Desai Architects**: Known for modern and sustainable designs.  \n\nThese architects and firms have significantly contributed to Pune's architecture, blending modernity with sustainability and cultural sensitivity. For specific projects or styles, it\u2019s best to explore their portfolios or reach out directly.",
